snippet.title: Pumpkin Curse teaser
snippet.description:
Pumpkin Curse

Jogo de plataforma 2D feito na jam Home of Nerds, organizada pelo site Itch.io e monitorada no Discord. Muitos jogos bons foram feitos nessas 62h e esse é o jogo do meu time, o Umizon. Espero que gostem. link para download no final da descrição.

English below:

A 2D plataform game made in the Home of Nerds Jam, hosted by HON at Discors, and organized by Itch.io. The Jam took 62h to finish, and a lot o grat games were made, this one was made by my team, Umizon.

Link to download the game: https://umizon.itch.io/pumpkin-curse

link to vote in the poll for best game: https://www.poll-maker.com/poll982280xe539e28E-41

link for all games made in the jam: https://www.homeofnerds.com/news/hon-game-jam-entries
